scenes.description: Gura chats with the audience about soy sauce, indigestion, and her plans to talk about hanging out with Watson later.
Gura reveals and discusses her new set of YouTube membership emotes, designed by the artist Mariette.
Gura begins discussing her desire to do something different for her birthday this year and addresses issues with the 'Ebi' emote not showing up.
